/-
# Tangent Bundles: Bibliography — L8 References

Key references in tangent bundle theory and differential geometry.
-/

import MiniTangentBundles.Core.Basic

namespace MiniTangentBundles

/-! ## Classic Texts — L8

1. **Spivak, M.** — "A Comprehensive Introduction to Differential Geometry" (5 vols)
   - Vol 1: Tangent vectors, bundles, and basic manifold theory
   
2. **Kobayashi, S. & Nomizu, K.** — "Foundations of Differential Geometry" (2 vols)
   - Vol 1: Connections, curvature, and tangent bundle geometry
   
3. **Warner, F.** — "Foundations of Differentiable Manifolds and Lie Groups"
   - Derivations approach to tangent vectors (Ch. 1)
   
4. **Lee, J.M.** — "Introduction to Smooth Manifolds" (2nd ed.)
   - Modern treatment of tangent bundles (Ch. 3-4)
   
5. **Hirsch, M.** — "Differential Topology"
   - Tangent bundles in differential topology context
   
6. **Milnor, J. & Stasheff, J.** — "Characteristic Classes"
   - Tangent bundle as a vector bundle; Stiefel-Whitney, Chern, Pontryagin classes
-/

/-! ## Advanced Texts — L9

7. **Besse, A.** — "Einstein Manifolds"
   - Riemannian geometry of tangent bundle; Sasaki metric
   
8. **Guillemin, V. & Sternberg, S.** — "Geometric Asymptotics"
   - Cotangent bundle in symplectic geometry and quantization
   
9. **Kolar, I., Michor, P., & Slovak, J.** — "Natural Operations in Differential Geometry"
   - Functorial approach to tangent bundles and jet bundles
   
10. **Mackenzie, K.** — "General Theory of Lie Groupoids and Lie Algebroids"
    - Tangent bundle as Lie algebroid; double structures
-/

/-! ## Research Articles

11. **Adams, J.F.** — "Vector Fields on Spheres" (Annals, 1962)
    - Solved the parallelizability problem using K-theory
    
12. **Atiyah, M.F. & Singer, I.M.** — "The Index of Elliptic Operators" (Annals, 1968)
    - Tangent bundle in index theory; Dirac operator on TM
    
13. **Bott, R.** — "Homogeneous Vector Bundles" (Annals, 1957)
    - Tangent bundles of homogeneous spaces G/H

14. **Eells, J. & Sampson, J.** — "Harmonic Mappings of Riemannian Manifolds" (1964)
    - Tangent bundle in the context of harmonic maps
-/

end MiniTangentBundles
